<p>
<strong>Control the PC with your mind!</strong>
</p>

<p>
A direct interface from your brain to your computer, and to the world!
</p>

<p>
It is an independent research project aimed at developing an
alternative input device based on BCI (Brain Control Interface): the
intended user is everyone unable to move, for permanent or temporary
impairment.  The solution is intended to be low cost and based on Open
Software.
</p>

